How to install this package:

1) git clone git://github.com/till/services_doingtext.git
2) cd services_doingtext
3) pear install -f --alldeps package.xml

Alternative:

1) pear install -f http://cloud.github.com/downloads/till/services_doingtext/Services_DoingText-0.1.0.tgz

(Replace 0.1.0 with the current release, I might forget to update the README!)

Notice

Version 0.1.0 -- breaks in BC are allowed. ;-)

